{"tid":1556303,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你我終於跳撚左閘！","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:33:25.000Z","uid":282721,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9d96decd1fb252f13ea405aca484c533f40a7dbc","tid":1556303,"uid":282721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"兩次都係喺欄杆死角位跳<br />\n鄭松泰式跳欄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uJk1Hni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJk1Hni.jpg&h=daec6455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但寶琳出閘好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQJCfEq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQJCfEq.jpg&h=2b779a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對高階foodpanda <br />\n瞄撚住欄杆位死角 等左10分鐘終於搵到機會跳<br />\n之後即跑 成個動作2秒都冇<br />\n<br />\n寶琳咁多foodpanda 自己一個人跳壓力好大 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我跳左啦 你又跳左未？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a24a3096d046042ca62d2651d8e497225c002fe","tid":1556303,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[全民和你唱]</span></span> 全世界全天候街邊唱香港國歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556100</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4a3a0f9454e72e4e67a2437e96a1c6aa43e8ef5","tid":1556303,"uid":39010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"宜家d 狗得閒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b6008ec4f7d2477575eb593420e3900c65fc0a","tid":1556303,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"